{"tid":2248495,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"15分鐘餸菜系列 - 日式蘿蔔炒豚肉片","createTime":"2020-10-18T15:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T04:42:51.000Z","uid":68594,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a184b1882755ae15594687bd177cff057f6b0d","tid":2248495,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"大家好啊！我係子言張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教大家整一個簡單啲嘅菜式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非常適合新手去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YIAHUfO0j2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYIAHUfO0j2w&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a9XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=4bc317c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YIAHUfO0j2w</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaafG73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaafG73.jpg&h=f2ff4f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔴材料<br />\n豚肉片......200克<br />\n白蘿蔔......半條<br />\n蔥..........少許<br />\n<br />\n🔴調味料<br />\n日本豉油、麻油、日本料理酒、胡椒粉、鹽、糖、雞粉、生粉<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n🔴步驟：<br />\n1.先切走白蘿蔔的頭部然後去皮，並把蘿蔔對半切開後一開四<br />\n2.把白蘿蔔全部切成薄片<br />\n3.豚肉片去冰後對半切開<br />\n4.把豚肉片調味:一圈日本料理酒、少許胡椒粉、一匙糖、兩至三圈生粉、半匙鹽、半匙雞粉，然後撈勻<br />\n5.用保鮮紙包好放入雪櫃冷藏30分鐘或以上<br />\n6.蔥沖洗乾淨後切成蔥花作備用<br />\n7.冷鑊落油，油熱後就可以放入豚肉片，煎至半熟<br />\n8.倒入蘿蔔片，把蘿蔔片炒至轉色及軟身<br />\n9.進行調味:兩蓋日本豉油，隨個人喜好倒入老抽及雞粉<br />\n10.醬汁煮至收乾後，可隨個人喜好加入蔥花，並撈勻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！我哋下一段片再見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n►訂閱我：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E5%AD%90%E8%A8%80%E5%BC%B5&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a9XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=98fae316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張</a>"},{"pid":"8cc22caa98bba1611eb3848f42894783c2ebbbaa","tid":2248495,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649c12e2e435152805641da886ccbb2b6dc6bd8b","tid":2248495,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cc22caa98bba1611eb3848f42894783c2ebbbaa","tid":2248495,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf8793ffdc78a97efce261968b469a20a26e280","tid":2248495,"uid":199776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"seem jeng"}]}